== Installation
	
		Install Eclipse MAT via the
		menu:
			<guimenu>Help[Install New Software...]
		menu entry.
		Select the update site of your release from the drop-down box and once its content is downloaded, select
		_General Purpose Tools_
		and its sub-entries
		_Memory Analyzer_
		and
		_Memory Analyzer(Charts)_
		.
	
	
